            </item><item>
                <title>Lighttpd 强制 Https 访问</title>
                <link>https://huan.ml/lighttps-force-https/</link>
                <pubDate>Wed, 24 Oct 2018 21:48:00 &#43;0000</pubDate>
                <author>驩讙懽歡</author>
                <guid>https://huan.ml/lighttps-force-https/</guid>
                <description>编辑lighttpd.conf文件，添加以下内容 1 2 3 4 5 6 #force https $SERVER[&amp;#34;socket&amp;#34;] == &amp;#34;:80&amp;#34; { $HTTP[&amp;#34;host&amp;#34;] =~ &amp;#34;([^:/]&#43;)&amp;#34; { url.redirect = ( &amp;#34;^/(.*)&amp;#34; =&amp;gt; &amp;#34;https://%0:443/$1&amp;#34; ) } } 即可。</description>
